WEBVTT

00:02.693 --> 00:06.564
and some scenes which some
viewers may find upsetting.

00:13.779 --> 00:15.498
Found you.

00:15.499 --> 00:17.178
Didn't know you were looking.

00:18.279 --> 00:20.478
Didn't realise you were leaving.

00:19.379 --> 00:20.779
Just for the weekend.

